{"tid":807078,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實天氣咁熱，點解啲女仲長髮披肩咁？","createTime":"2018-09-05T08:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T11:57:19.000Z","uid":42174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ccfd9deb5a829129a5b25967bf5c7ac51eacf07a","tid":807078,"uid":42174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"三十幾度仲要咁焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一諗到頭髮下面成頸汗就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔好好地紮住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7233490f640d4b2047769b48cfb479b4fe22e0c","tid":807078,"uid":42174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae0a319d0813fef1f164c42538399f380d9a9cb","tid":807078,"uid":42174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a827ad5fc894cce640fa55e526354d6f2a96f0","tid":807078,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:52:43.000Z","msg":"剪"},{"pid":"fb95a8eb8684d8b62b809b3325fe06458746131e","tid":807078,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"井上推論，男女耐熱力的差異，可能是因為女性的體液少於男性，比較容易脫水，所以採取減少排汗量的方式來適應高溫的環境，而男性為了能更有效地從事長時間的運動或勞動，因此採用提高排汗量的適應策略。<br />\n<br />\n不過研究者建議，不論男性或女性，在熱浪來襲之前應保持規律運動，有助於適應炎熱的氣候。英國利物浦約翰摩爾斯大學教授凱博(Tim Cable)解釋，流汗是好事，可加速身體散熱，然而婦女很可能是透過其他身體機制散熱，例如皮膚，因為它的表面積較大。"}]}